A BACKUP GENERATOR.

14:41.267 --> 14:43.700
THIS PUMP WILL PROVIDE YOU
WITH A MORPHINE DRIP,

14:43.733 --> 14:45.633
AND IT SHOULD STOP YOUR PAIN.

14:45.667 --> 14:47.567
