15:16.567 --> 15:19.200
ANNA, WE'RE TALKING ABOUT
YOUR ABILITY TO EVER WALK AGAIN.

15:19.233 --> 15:21.133
THAT'S WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

15:21.167 --> 15:23.067
