THAT ARE WAY OLD

15:27.667 --> 15:29.567
AND WAY SET IN STONE
AND WAY SPIRITUAL,

15:29.600 --> 15:31.567
AND YOU DON'T MESS WITH THEM.

15:31.600 --> 15:34.733
YOU DON'T
ANGER THE ANCESTORS...

15:34.767 --> 15:37.500
EVEN IF YOU PIERCE YOUR TONGUE
AND PLAY IN A BAND.

15:37.533 --> 15:40.667
WHAT ARE THE RULES EXACTLY?

15:43.733 --> 15:45.500
ALL I.C.U. PATIENTS ARE GOIN'
TO THE SOUTH WING.

15:45.533 --> 15:48.367
ALL TELEMETRY AND STEP-DOWN
PATIENTS, NORTH WING.
YOU PAGED ME.

15:48.400 --> 15:51.200
PORN AS PAIN MANAGEMENT?
YOU MET HENRY.
YEAH, THERE ARE

15:51.233 --> 15:53.167
