WENT JUST FINE.

16:37.067 --> 16:38.233
IS THAT MUCH BRUISING NORMAL?

16:38.267 --> 16:40.600
YOUR WOUND LOOKS GOOD,
MRS. BRADLEY,

16:40.633 --> 16:42.100
AND SO DO THE RESULTS
ON YOUR CATH.

16:42.133 --> 16:43.800
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY BLOCKAGE
IN YOUR ARTERIES.

16:43.833 --> 16:46.467
