YOU DEFINITELY DID NOT HAVE
A HEART ATTACK.

16:46.500 --> 16:47.667
OH HO HO.

16:47.700 --> 16:50.133
SO I CAN GO HOME?

16:50.167 --> 16:52.333
NOT YET.
YOUR E.K.G. SHOWS

16:52.367 --> 16:54.100
SIGNIFICANT CHANGES,

16:54.133 --> 16:57.367
