FOR A HEALING RITUAL?

18:26.800 --> 18:28.700
WHEN SICKNESS COMES,
IT MEANS THAT

18:28.733 --> 18:30.367
ONE OF OUR SOULS
IS MISSING.

18:30.400 --> 18:32.300
ANNA NEEDS
TO HAVE HER SOULS INTACT

18:32.333 --> 18:35.100
BEFORE SHE HAS SURGERY.
SHE NEEDS A SHAMAN.

18:35.133 --> 18:37.067
