THE FACT THAT I'M TELLING YOU

18:47.500 --> 18:49.433
ANNA NEEDS THE SURGERY
IN THE NEXT 24 HOURS

18:49.467 --> 18:51.333
IF SHE'S GOING TO CONTINUE
TO WALK.

18:51.367 --> 18:53.267
