YOUR BUTT, CHIEF.

19:53.200 --> 19:55.100
YOU DIDN'T AUTHORIZE
THE REPLACEMENT GENERATOR,

19:55.133 --> 19:57.567
SAVING MONEY
FOR THE NEW M.R.I. MACHINE.

19:57.600 --> 20:03.200
