BURKE IS TALKING
GEORGE AND ALEX

21:00.833 --> 21:02.733
THROUGH HEART SURGERY
IN THE ELEVATOR.

21:02.767 --> 21:04.667
SHEPHERD'S SETTING UP
A SHAMAN HEALING RITUAL.

21:04.700 --> 21:06.600
ROCK ON.

21:06.633 --> 21:09.200
I HAVE PORN GUY.

21:10.367 --> 21:11.633
