21:11.667 --> 21:14.400
MR. LAMOTT,
WHAT'S WRONG?

21:14.433 --> 21:15.333
(groans)

21:15.367 --> 21:18.333
YOUR PRESSURE'S ELEVATED.

21:18.367 --> 21:19.833
