21:32.200 --> 21:34.233
OH, OKAY. OKAY.

21:36.500 --> 21:38.167
YOU'RE ALLERGIC
TO MOST NARCOTICS

21:38.200 --> 21:39.533
AND NSAIDS.

21:39.567 --> 21:42.800
