AND DEEP.

23:17.700 --> 23:20.367
USE THE SCISSORS
IF YOU HAVE TO.
OKAY.

23:20.400 --> 23:23.333
BUT BE SURE YOU DON'T CUT
INTO THE LUNG OR HEART.

23:23.367 --> 23:24.567
