OF THAT?

23:24.600 --> 23:27.367
YOU JUST HAVE TO BE SURE.

23:27.400 --> 23:32.067
***

23:36.767 --> 23:40.633
WE'RE NOT IN KANSAS ANYMORE.

23:58.467 --> 24:00.733
YOUR SHAMAN'S LATE.

24:00.767 --> 24:02.533
MY SHAMAN IS NEVER LATE.

24:06.833 --> 24:07.867
