THE STEADIEST HANDS.

24:10.233 --> 24:11.167
IZZIE.

24:11.200 --> 24:12.133
YEAH.

24:12.167 --> 24:15.067
HE CAN HEAR YOU.

24:15.100 --> 24:16.600
(Burke) O'MALLEY...

24:16.633 --> 24:19.600
HOW YOU DOIN' DOWN THERE?

24:19.633 --> 24:22.200
UH,
THE FIRE DEPARTMENT'S HERE.

24:22.233 --> 24:24.333
THEY CAN GET THE DOORS OPEN.
NO. NOBODY MOVES.

24:24.367 --> 24:26.067
NOBODY WORKS ON THE ELEVATOR.

24:26.100 --> 24:27.267
I HAVE AN OPEN CHEST

24:27.300 --> 24:29.367
AND A VERY NERVOUS INTERN
IN THERE.

24:29.400 --> 24:32.167
KEEP THEM BACK
UNTIL I GIVE THE WORD.
OKAY, GUYS, WE'RE NOT...

24:32.200 --> 24:32.967
O'MALLEY...

24:33.067 --> 24:35.067
I DIDN'T CUT THE HEART
OR THE LUNGS.

24:35.100 --> 24:37.533
DR. BURKE, I DIDN'T CUT
THE HEART OR THE LUNGS.

24:37.567 --> 24:39.467
OKAY, GOOD, GOOD.
GOOD, O'MALLEY. REALLY GOOD.

24:39.500 --> 24:42.067
NOW CHECK FOR INJURIES
AND DO A PERICARDIOTOMY.

24:42.067 --> 24:44.400
I'LL NEED SOME LAP PADS,

24:44.433 --> 24:48.167
FORCEPS, METZENBAUMS
AND SATINSKY CLAMPS.

24:49.567 --> 24:52.133
YES, YOU WILL.

24:52.167 --> 24:54.133
YOU TELL ANYONE
I DID THIS FOR YOU,

24:54.167 --> 24:56.067
NOT ONLY WILL I KILL YOU,

24:56.100 --> 24:58.067
I WILL SELL YOUR BODY PARTS
FOR CASH.

24:58.100 --> 24:59.567
UH-HUH.

24:59.600 --> 25:03.067
OKAY. SO...

25:03.100 --> 25:05.800
THERE WERE THESE WOMEN--
NURSES--

25:05.833 --> 25:07.500
THREE NURSES--
MM-HMM.

25:07.533 --> 25:11.067
AND THEY WERE...
NAUGHTY.

25:11.067 --> 25:13.100
THEY'RE REALLY,
REALLY NAUGHTY.

25:13.133 --> 25:14.533
THEY WERE THREE
NAUGHTY NURSES.

25:14.567 --> 25:16.467
SAUCY EVEN--
THEY WERE SAUCY

25:16.500 --> 25:19.200
AND BAD AND NAUGHTY.

25:19.233 --> 25:20.733
THREE SAUCY, BAD,
NAUGHTY NURSES--

25:20.767 --> 25:23.767
THEY WERE TAKING
A SHOWER TOGETHER.

25:23.800 --> 25:25.467
SOAPING EACH OTHER UP,

25:25.500 --> 25:27.767
AND THEN THIS DOCTOR
WALKS IN,

25:27.800 --> 25:31.233
AND HE SEES THESE THREE
NAUGHTY, BAD NURSES

25:31.267 --> 25:34.100
WITH THESE GREAT BIG...

25:34.133 --> 25:36.067
MRS. BRADLEY, DO YOU REALIZE
THAT YOU'VE BEEN

25:36.067 --> 25:37.800
ADMITTED TO THE HOSPITAL
ON THIS DATE

25:37.833 --> 25:40.067
FOR THE PAST SEVEN YEARS?

25:40.100 --> 25:41.067
OH, THAT CAN'T BE.

25:41.067 --> 25:43.100
I DON'T REMEMBER THE DATE
EXACTLY, BUT--

25:43.133 --> 25:44.600
I HAVE THE MEDICAL RECORDS.

25:44.633 --> 25:46.700
ON THIS DATE
FOR THE PAST SEVEN YEARS,

25:46.733 --> 25:48.633
YOU HAVE WHAT LOOKS LIKE
A HEART ATTACK.

25:48.667 --> 25:50.333
NO. NO.

25:50.367 --> 25:53.467
I KNOW I'VE HAD SOME SCARES,
BUT I DON'T--

25:53.500 --> 25:54.667
EVERY YEAR ON THIS DATE?

25:54.700 --> 25:58.600
IS THERE SOME SIGNIFICANCE
TO THIS DATE FOR YOU PERSONALLY?

25:58.633 --> 26:01.067
NO. NOTHIN'.

26:01.100 --> 26:02.800
WHAT WERE YOU DOING
THE FIRST YEAR,

26:02.833 --> 26:04.333
THE FIRST TIME YOU HAD
A CARDIAC EPISODE?

26:04.367 --> 26:06.300
OH, WHO CAN REMEMBER
BACK THAT FAR?

26:06.333 --> 26:08.633
WE WERE IN THE YARD. I REMEMBER
BECAUSE OUR NEIGHBOR--

26:08.667 --> 26:10.567
WHAT WAS HIS NAME?
TED.

26:10.600 --> 26:12.733
THAT'S RIGHT. HE DIED.

26:12.767 --> 26:14.567
OF AN ANEURYSM, I THINK.

26:14.600 --> 26:16.567
AND WE WATCHED
AS THE FUNERAL HOME PEOPLE

26:16.600 --> 26:18.267
TOOK HIM AWAY,

26:18.300 --> 26:20.200
AND YOU HAD
YOUR FIRST ATTACK.

26:20.233 --> 26:22.267
AND YOU WERE CLOSE
TO TED?

26:22.300 --> 26:24.733
NO. OH, WE BARELY KNEW TED.

26:24.767 --> 26:26.267
WELL, THAT WAS ALL VERY SAD,

26:26.300 --> 26:28.833
BUT WHAT DOES THAT HAVE TO DO
WITH VERNA'S HEART?

26:28.867 --> 26:32.200
***

26:33.500 --> 26:35.833
I REMOVED A SMALL CLOT
FROM THE PERICARDIUM.

26:35.867 --> 26:38.533
NO OBVIOUS CARDIAC INJURIES.

26:38.567 --> 26:40.367
ANY CHANGE IN THE VITALS?

26:40.400 --> 26:42.167
(Alex) B.P.'s STILL TOO LOW
TO REGISTER ON THE MONITOR.

26:42.200 --> 26:44.233
WE NEED TO CROSS-CLAMP
THE AORTA.

26:44.267 --> 26:47.133
***

26:47.167 --> 26:51.233
STICK YOUR HAND IN
AND BLUNTLY DISSECT DOWN

26:51.267 --> 26:53.500
UNTIL YOU FEEL
TWO TUBE-LIKE STRUCTURES.

26:53.533 --> 26:55.567
THE ESOPHAGUS WILL BE
MORE MEDIAL AND ANTERIOR.

26:55.600 --> 26:58.500
UM, I FEEL ONE TUBE
THAT'S EASILY COLLAPSIBLE,

26:58.533 --> 27:02.700
AND THE OTHER'S, UH,
MORE MUSCULAR

27:02.733 --> 27:04.367
AND SPONGY.

27:04.400 --> 27:06.800
I CAN FEEL THE SPINE
JUST UNDERNEATH IT.

27:06.833 --> 27:08.467
YES! YOU'RE TOUCHING
THE AORTA.

27:08.500 --> 27:11.167
I'M TOUCHING THE AORTA.

27:11.200 --> 27:14.200
WRAP THE INDEX FINGER
OF YOUR LEFT HAND AROUND IT

27:14.233 --> 27:17.100
AND APPLY A SATINSKY CLAMP
WITH YOUR RIGHT HAND.

27:17.133 --> 27:20.567
***

27:22.733 --> 27:24.533
GOT IT.

27:24.567 --> 27:27.400
WAIT, I-I THINK
I CAN LOCALIZE THE BLEEDING.

27:27.433 --> 27:29.600
I THINK IT'S COMING FROM
THE INFERIOR VENA CAVA.

27:29.633 --> 27:31.167
CAN YOU FIND THE LESION?

27:31.200 --> 27:33.133
YEAH.

27:33.167 --> 27:35.300
YEAH, I THINK I CAN FEEL IT.

27:35.333 --> 27:37.233
IT'S TOO FAR IN
TO REPAIR.

27:37.267 --> 27:38.833
HOW BIG IS IT?
SMALL.

27:38.867 --> 27:41.467
MAYBE SMALLER THAN A DIME.

27:41.500 --> 27:44.533
OKAY, O'MALLEY, I WANT YOU
TO TAKE YOUR FINGER

27:44.567 --> 27:46.467
AND PLUG THE HOLE.

27:47.800 --> 27:52.100
I THINK I CAN FEEL HIS HEART
STARTING TO FILL MORE.

27:52.133 --> 27:54.167
IT'S BEATING
A LITTLE STRONGER.

27:54.200 --> 27:57.300
EXCELLENT.
KEEP YOUR FINGER THERE.
OKAY. NOW WHAT?

27:57.333 --> 27:59.267
THAT'S IT.

27:59.300 --> 28:00.800
THAT'S IT?

28:04.067 --> 28:05.567
(George) I JUST STAND HERE

28:05.600 --> 28:07.500
WITH MY FINGER
PLUGGING THE HOLE?

28:07.533 --> 28:09.433
UNTIL WE CAN GET YOU
OUT OF THAT ELEVATOR

28:09.467 --> 28:11.133
AND INTO THE O.R.

28:11.167 --> 28:12.400
DR. BAILEY,

28:12.433 --> 28:16.133
YOU CAN TELL THE FIREMEN
TO GET MY GUYS OUTTA THERE.
WILL DO.

28:16.167 --> 28:19.067
OKAY, WE'RE READY.

28:19.100 --> 28:20.267
O'MALLEY.

28:20.300 --> 28:21.600
YES, SIR.

28:21.633 --> 28:23.800
YOU JUST FLEW SOLO.

28:25.533 --> 28:28.533
THANK YOU, SIR.

28:28.567 --> 28:31.800
***

28:38.333 --> 28:41.067
OKAY, ANNA, WE'RE GONNA
SHUT OFF THE P.C.A. PUMP NOW,

28:41.100 --> 28:42.433
WHICH MEANS YOU'LL BE
IN A LOT OF PAIN

28:42.467 --> 28:43.833
FOR THE DURATION OF THE--

28:43.867 --> 28:45.200
THE HEALING RITUAL.

28:45.233 --> 28:46.733
ARE YOU OKAY WITH THAT?

28:46.767 --> 28:50.633
YEAH. I CAN'T FIND MY SOUL
IF I'M MEDICATED.

28:50.667 --> 28:52.667
NO PAIN, NO GAIN, RIGHT?

28:52.700 --> 28:55.467
IT'S NOT JUST FOR YOUR FATHER.
YOU BELIEVE IT, TOO, RIGHT?

28:55.500 --> 28:57.400
I KNOW IT SOUNDS
LIKE A LOAD OF CRAP,

28:57.433 --> 28:59.367
BUT WATCH THE RITUAL,
YOU'LL SEE.

28:59.400 --> 29:00.600
SEE WHAT?

29:00.633 --> 29:02.800
THE MOMENT IT HAPPENS.

29:05.433 --> 29:08.333
***

29:21.300 --> 29:24.500
I'M READY.

29:29.867 --> 29:33.800
"OH, YES, I'M SO VERY,
VERY NAUGHTY,"

29:33.833 --> 29:34.800
BIANCA SAID

29:34.833 --> 29:37.433
AS SHE, UH, DROPPED
HER STETHOSCOPE.

29:37.467 --> 29:39.833
"ME, TOO," SAID CRYSTAL

29:39.867 --> 29:42.167
AS SHE SNAPPED ON
HER SURGICAL GLOVE,

29:42.200 --> 29:45.400
AND THEN THERE WAS MARTA...

29:54.567 --> 29:55.733
WHERE WAS I?

29:55.767 --> 29:57.700
MARTA.

29:57.733 --> 30:00.367
OH, YES. MARTA WAS
THE NAUGHTIEST NURSE OF ALL

30:00.400 --> 30:02.267
BECAUSE SHE KNEW HOW TO--

30:02.300 --> 30:03.467
(Woman giggling)

30:03.500 --> 30:05.167
OH, THANK GOD.

30:05.200 --> 30:06.367
(giggling continues)

30:06.400 --> 30:07.700
(Man) WE'RE BACK UP.

30:07.733 --> 30:10.633
***

30:17.600 --> 30:19.500
HOW LONG
DO YOU THINK IT TAKES

30:19.533 --> 30:21.633
TO RETRIEVE A LOST SOUL?

30:26.300 --> 30:28.433
I DON'T KNOW.

30:28.467 --> 30:30.500
WAY TO GO, GEORGE.

30:30.533 --> 30:32.500
I HAVE MY FINGER
IN A HEART.

30:32.533 --> 30:34.333
VERY COOL.

30:34.367 --> 30:37.267
***

30:47.433 --> 30:49.600
YOU HAVE
STRESS CARDIOMYOPATHY.

30:49.633 --> 30:53.133
CARDIOMYOPATHY? WHAT--CAN YOU
TELL ME WHAT THAT IS?

30:53.167 --> 30:54.600
IT'S TED.

30:54.633 --> 30:57.133
TED?

30:57.167 --> 30:58.467
TED.

30:58.500 --> 31:00.667
NOT JUST A NEIGHBOR
YOU BARELY KNEW, WAS HE?

31:00.700 --> 31:03.333
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

31:03.367 --> 31:05.267
BECAUSE EVERY YEAR
ON THE DAY HE DIED,

31:05.300 --> 31:08.100
YOU GET A RUSH OF ADRENALINE
CAUSED BY STRESS.

31:08.133 --> 31:12.233
YOUR PRESSURE RISES,
YOU HAVE CHEST PAINS...

31:12.267 --> 31:15.200
AND YOU END UP HERE.

31:16.433 --> 31:19.567
27 YEARS...

31:19.600 --> 31:24.200
I LOVED THE MAN NEXT DOOR
AND HE LOVED ME.

31:24.233 --> 31:26.600
I KNOW
HOW THIS IS GONNA SOUND...

31:26.633 --> 31:29.233
TED WAS MY SOUL MATE.

31:31.433 --> 31:34.333
AND THEN HE JUST DIED.

31:34.367 --> 31:36.400
IT'S GRIEF.

31:36.433 --> 31:38.100
YOUR HEART STOPS

31:38.133 --> 31:40.367
BECAUSE YOU'RE GRIEVING
FOR TED.

31:40.400 --> 31:42.767
SO...

31:42.800 --> 31:44.300
WHAT DO I DO NEXT?

31:44.333 --> 31:47.767
I MEAN,
HOW DO YOU TREAT IT?

31:50.600 --> 31:53.400
I WISH I KNEW.

31:53.433 --> 31:56.333
***

32:31.133 --> 32:33.600
I TOLD THATCH
I'M LEAVING HIM.

32:33.633 --> 32:35.600
YOU LEFT THATCHER, ELLIS.

32:35.633 --> 32:38.467
BUT I COULDN'T BRING MYSELF
TO LEAVE ADELE.

32:38.500 --> 32:40.400
DO YOU REMEMBER?

32:42.467 --> 32:44.467
PAINTED HORSES...

32:44.500 --> 32:47.133
YES.

32:47.167 --> 32:49.067
WE WERE ON THE CAROUSEL
IN THE PARK.

32:49.100 --> 32:50.800
IT WAS RAINING.

32:50.833 --> 32:52.800
I HAVE AN OFFER
FROM BOSTON GENERAL.

32:52.833 --> 32:55.067
YOU TOOK IT TO GET AWAY.

32:55.067 --> 32:56.800
WE SWORE
WE'D NEVER TALK AGAIN

32:56.833 --> 32:58.733
ABOUT WHAT WE HAD TOGETHER.

32:58.767 --> 33:01.200
IT WAS GONNA ALWAYS BE
OUR SECRET.

33:01.233 --> 33:02.167
RICHARD...

33:02.200 --> 33:05.300
YES, ELLIS.

33:05.333 --> 33:07.600
CAROUSELS GIVE ME
THE CREEPS.

33:10.433 --> 33:12.233
HOW DO YOU PUT UP
WITH IT?

33:12.267 --> 33:15.333
I MEAN,
"NASTY, NAUGHTY NURSES 4,"

33:15.367 --> 33:17.333
AND I'M ASSUMING
1, 2 AND 3?

33:17.367 --> 33:18.633
HE'S MY HENRY.

33:18.667 --> 33:20.567
I KNOW,
BUT DON'T YOU FIND IT

33:20.600 --> 33:22.467
MISOGYNISTIC AND DEGRADING
AND KIND OF...

33:22.500 --> 33:27.700
24 HOURS A DAY OF PORN?
SERIOUSLY, THAT'S YOUR LIFE?

33:27.733 --> 33:30.367
I'M GRATEFUL FOR IT.
IT TAKES AWAY HIS PAIN.

33:30.400 --> 33:32.267
AND SEE, THE THING IS,

33:32.300 --> 33:35.800
HENRY--HENRY TAKES AWAY
MY PAIN.

33:35.833 --> 33:38.733
***

34:41.133 --> 34:42.467
I LIED.

34:42.500 --> 34:45.367
I'M NOT OUT
OF THIS RELATIONSHIP.

34:45.400 --> 34:47.767
I'M IN. I'M SO IN
IT'S HUMILIATING

34:47.800 --> 34:49.300
BECAUSE HERE I AM
BEGGING--

34:49.333 --> 34:51.133
MEREDITH, JUST--
SHUT UP.

34:51.167 --> 34:53.067
YOU SAY "MEREDITH,"
AND I YELL, REMEMBER?

34:53.067 --> 34:53.833
YEAH.

34:53.867 --> 34:55.400
OKAY...

34:55.433 --> 34:57.500
HERE IT IS.

34:57.533 --> 34:59.667
YOUR CHOICE, IT'S SIMPLE--

34:59.700 --> 35:02.200
HER OR ME.

35:02.233 --> 35:04.633
AND I'M SURE
SHE'S REALLY GREAT.

35:04.667 --> 35:08.200
BUT, DEREK, I LOVE YOU...

35:08.233 --> 35:12.167
IN A REALLY, REALLY BIG...

35:12.200 --> 35:14.367
PRETEND TO LIKE YOUR TASTE
IN MUSIC,

35:14.400 --> 35:17.100
LET YOU EAT THE LAST PIECE
OF CHEESECAKE,

35:17.133 --> 35:19.833
HOLD A RADIO OVER MY HEAD
OUTSIDE YOUR WINDOW,

35:19.867 --> 35:22.267
UNFORTUNATE WAY
THAT MAKES ME HATE YOU

35:22.300 --> 35:23.633
LOVE YOU.

35:23.667 --> 35:25.167
SO PICK ME.

35:25.200 --> 35:27.467
CHOOSE ME.

35:27.500 --> 35:30.067
LOVE ME.

35:33.433 --> 35:35.333
I'LL BE AT JOE'S TONIGHT,

35:35.367 --> 35:38.700
SO IF YOU DO DECIDE
TO SIGN THE PAPERS...

35:38.733 --> 35:41.433
MEET ME THERE.

36:09.433 --> 36:12.200
GOOD-BYE, ELLIS.

36:16.133 --> 36:18.133
I AM GONNA COME
SEE YOU TOMORROW.

36:18.167 --> 36:19.733
OKAY?

36:19.767 --> 36:22.133
HE DOESN'T LOVE HER.

36:23.667 --> 36:25.567
HE CAN'T.

36:25.600 --> 36:27.500
BUT HE'LL STAY
WITH HER ANYWAY.

36:27.533 --> 36:30.300
SHE'S HIS WIFE.

36:30.333 --> 36:31.500
MOM?

36:34.433 --> 36:35.767
MOMMY?

36:35.800 --> 36:38.733
MEREDITH...

36:38.767 --> 36:40.100
YOU GREW UP.

36:40.133 --> 36:41.600
I DID.

36:41.633 --> 36:44.100
HMM. IT'S A SHAME.

36:44.133 --> 36:46.600
IT'S AWFUL
BEING A GROWN-UP.

36:46.633 --> 36:49.067
BUT THE CAROUSEL
NEVER STOPS TURNING.

36:50.533 --> 36:52.567
YOU CAN'T GET OFF.

36:56.067 --> 36:58.367
OKAY.

37:02.767 --> 37:06.767
***

37:10.533 --> 37:12.367
YOU THINK HE'LL SHOW?

37:12.400 --> 37:14.533
HE'LL SHOW.

37:18.167 --> 37:20.233
(bell on door jingles)

37:20.267 --> 37:21.300
HEY.

37:21.333 --> 37:25.067
***

37:29.800 --> 37:31.433
HOW'S YOUR PATIENT?

37:31.467 --> 37:33.367
THE ONE THAT GOT
HER SOUL BACK?

37:33.400 --> 37:35.433
SHE'S GONNA BE FINE.

37:35.467 --> 37:36.767
HEY. GOTTA GO.

37:36.800 --> 37:39.233
LOOK AT YOU.
YOU LOOK LIKE A GIRL.

37:39.267 --> 37:40.300
IS THAT YOUR DATE?

37:40.333 --> 37:41.833
IT'S MY HUSBAND.

37:41.867 --> 37:43.200
YOU'RE MARRIED?

37:43.233 --> 37:44.733
TEN YEARS TODAY.

37:44.767 --> 37:47.400
HOW COME I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE MARRIED.

37:47.433 --> 37:49.167
YOU NEVER ASKED.

37:50.800 --> 37:53.533
YOU HAVEN'T SIGNED
THOSE DIVORCE PAPERS YET,

37:53.567 --> 37:55.567
HAVE YOU?

37:55.600 --> 37:57.333
BAILEY...

37:57.367 --> 37:58.433
TELL ME WHAT TO DO.

37:58.467 --> 38:00.433
(laughs)

38:00.467 --> 38:03.067
GOD. WHY DOES THIS
HAVE TO BE SO HARD?

38:03.100 --> 38:04.267
IT'S NOT HARD.

38:04.300 --> 38:07.133
IT'S PAINFUL,
BUT IT'S NOT HARD.

38:07.167 --> 38:09.067
COME ON, YOU KNOW
WHAT TO DO ALREADY.

38:09.100 --> 38:10.267
IF YOU DIDN'T,

38:10.300 --> 38:12.600
YOU WOULDN'T BE
IN SO MUCH PAIN.

38:19.500 --> 38:21.733
PAIN--

38:21.767 --> 38:23.667
YOU JUST HAVE TO
RIDE IT OUT,

38:23.700 --> 38:26.267
HOPE IT GOES AWAY
ON ITS OWN,

38:26.300 --> 38:28.333
HOPE THE WOUND
THAT CAUSED IT HEALS.

38:28.367 --> 38:31.133
SO...
HERE'S WHERE WE ARE.

38:31.167 --> 38:33.067
I WORK TOO MUCH,
I'M COMPETITIVE,

38:33.100 --> 38:34.600
I'M ALWAYS RIGHT.

38:34.633 --> 38:35.800
AND I SNORE.

38:35.833 --> 38:37.233
WHAT?

38:38.533 --> 38:40.467
I'M TRYING HERE.

38:40.500 --> 38:42.400
OH. OH.

38:42.433 --> 38:44.233
OH! OH.

38:44.267 --> 38:46.733
YEAH.

38:46.767 --> 38:48.700
SO?

38:51.300 --> 38:53.500
WHATEVER. DON'T MAKE
A BIG DEAL ABOUT IT.

39:05.300 --> 39:07.500
THERE ARE NO SOLUTIONS,

39:07.533 --> 39:10.167
NO EASY ANSWERS.

39:10.200 --> 39:13.600
YOU JUST BREATHE DEEP
AND WAIT FOR IT TO SUBSIDE.

39:13.633 --> 39:16.167
OH, MAN!
I JUST--I CAN'T--

39:16.200 --> 39:18.133
(bell on door jingles)

39:18.167 --> 39:21.733
***

39:21.767 --> 39:23.167
HE'S NOT COMING.

39:24.700 --> 39:26.667
YOU DON'T THINK
HE'S COMING.

39:26.700 --> 39:29.200
HE MIGHT COME.

39:29.233 --> 39:31.500
YEAH. YOU NEVER KNOW.

39:31.533 --> 39:32.500
HE'S DEFINITELY COMING.
(kicks George under bar)

39:32.533 --> 39:35.067
OW! YOU WANT HER DOING
TEQUILA SHOTS ALL NIGHT?

39:35.100 --> 39:36.833
I'LL BE THE ONE
CLEANING UP THE VOMIT.

39:36.867 --> 39:39.767
BESIDES, I TOUCHED
A HEART TODAY...

39:39.800 --> 39:41.067
PORNY.

39:43.367 --> 39:45.200
(bell on door jingles)

39:51.333 --> 39:53.267
MOST OF THE TIME,
PAIN CAN BE MANAGED.

39:56.500 --> 39:58.167
POUR ME ANOTHER ONE.

39:58.200 --> 40:00.200
BUT SOMETIMES,
THE PAIN GETS YOU

40:00.233 --> 40:01.700
WHEN YOU LEAST EXPECT IT...

40:01.733 --> 40:05.100
I'M TELLIN' YOU,
ANY SECOND.

40:05.133 --> 40:07.800
HITS WAY BELOW THE BELT

40:07.833 --> 40:09.467
AND DOESN'T LET UP.

40:09.500 --> 40:13.600
***

40:13.633 --> 40:17.567
I HAVE BEEN LOOKING
EVERYWHERE FOR YOU.

40:17.600 --> 40:20.833
WELL...

40:20.867 --> 40:22.200
YOU FOUND ME.

40:22.233 --> 40:23.333
SO...

40:23.367 --> 40:27.133
YOU GONNA SIGN
THOSE DIVORCE PAPERS OR NOT?

40:27.167 --> 40:28.600
***

40:28.633 --> 40:30.533
PAIN--

40:30.567 --> 40:32.467
YOU JUST HAVE TO
FIGHT THROUGH

40:32.500 --> 40:35.467
BECAUSE THE TRUTH IS,
YOU CAN'T OUTRUN IT

40:35.500 --> 40:38.667
AND LIFE ALWAYS MAKES MORE.

40:38.700 --> 40:41.600
***
